# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HEXA-OLIGONUCLEOTIDE.tape — architecture-current (editable per v1.2)
# OLIGONUCLEOTIDE axis · EXPANSION-MAIN layer (NOT core-5)
# Event history → HEXA-OLIGONUCLEOTIDE.log.tape sibling (if/when needed)
